      "content": "Access end-of-day historical OHLCV data for stocks, ETFs, funds, indices, and currencies across global exchanges. Returns daily, weekly, or monthly historical price and volume data with both raw and split/dividend-adjusted closing prices.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: EODHD Support",
